read the last sentence

00:49:18.333 --> 00:49:18.900
Anita: Ouch.

00:49:18.900 --> 00:49:22.934
female: And that's no, just the sentence
and that's like a good indication

00:49:22.934 --> 00:49:25.133
of if you're probably gonna
