00:49:32.633 --> 00:49:35.567
Anita: It's the first thing I always check.

00:49:35.567 --> 00:49:39.600
female: But I was wondering if you have
any tidbits of advice like that.

00:49:39.600 --> 00:49:43.400
Anita: No, I will give any book
